data.description: OWNER SAYS SELL! DUE TO RELOCATION!   BUYER ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT JUST 5.625%!  No flood Insurance required and no costly HOA fees! Enjoy your light and bright, high and dry expanded Lanai and take in the fresh outdoor air and colorful sunsets, while entertaining poolside with friends and family. With almost 2000 square feet of living space, you will LOVE to grill to your hearts content in this pristine 3 bedroom, + Den, 2 bathroom Pool home. Close to shopping including, FGCU, RSW Airport, restaurants, Coconut Point, Gulf Coast TC, Miromar Outlets, Beaches and more! This sunny and open floor plan beauty, sits on a fenced-in, private lot. Features include: New Roof (2023), Newer Energy Efficient HVAC (2022), Newer Fence (2020), Newer Septic (2017), New Pool Pump (2023), Vaulted Ceilings, Diagonal Tile, Oversized Kitchen, Remodeled Bathrooms with Pool Bath, Large Primary Suite with Her/His Closets, Wainscotting, Custom Built-in Shelving, Storm Garage Door, Fresh Paint, Oversized Screened Lanai, Custom Blinds, Designer Lighting and Fans and plenty of Storage Space!  This is where happy memories are made. All the major work is done. Please call to schedule your appointment today.
